&lt;h2 id="road-directions-from-warren-house-inn-towards-moretonhampstead"&gt;Road Directions from Warren House Inn (towards Moretonhampstead)
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take 1st road on LEFT – route to Fernworthy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pass Jurston Farm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Yellands Crossroads – TURN LEFT&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pass left turn to Lower Corndon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pass right turn and then ttake HAIRPIN LEFT to Fernworthy - use the layby to turn the car!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pass a left turn to Higher Corndon&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take RIGHT turn and pass Collihole Farm, Hole Farm and Cullaton to T-junction, turn LEFT to THORN&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pass THORN and go to YEO FARM&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At Yeo Farm bear RIGHT to TEIGNCOMBE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive through Teigncombe to the end of the road&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The end-of-the-road car park is marked with the yellow cross.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="parking"&gt;Parking
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;There is a small parking area at the given coordinates. The approach roads to Batworthy are quite long and narrow, although rarely busy.&lt;/p&gt;
